  "remarks": "\nAndrei Sergeevich Mandel is an involved person under The Sudan (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2020 through his association with M-Invest, which acts as a front for the Wagner Group, and which is itself an involved person as it is responsible for action, policy or activity which threatens the peace, stability and security of Sudan. \n",
